import React from 'react'
import {ServicesContainer, ServicesH1, ServicesH2, ServicesP, ServicesIcon, ServicesCard, ServicesWrapper} from './ServiceElements'
import {ReactComponent as Icon1} from '../../images/1.svg'
import {ReactComponent as Icon2} from '../../images/2.svg'


const Services = () => {
    return (
        <ServicesContainer id="services">
        <ServicesH1>My Interests</ServicesH1>
        <ServicesWrapper>
            <ServicesCard>
                <Icon1 />
                <ServicesH2>Robotics and Automation</ServicesH2>
                <ServicesP>Enhancing physical elements of living.</ServicesP>
            </ServicesCard>
            <ServicesCard>
                <ServicesIcon src={Icon2} />
                <ServicesH2>Machine Learning and Data Analytics</ServicesH2>
                <ServicesP></ServicesP>
            </ServicesCard>
        </ServicesWrapper>
        </ServicesContainer>
    )
}

export default Services
